title: SC EP:354 Hey look! A Monkey!
itunes:title: SC EP:354 Hey look! A Monkey!
description: Tonight I will be speaking to Josh who had a strange encounter while out camping in Canada. Many shows ago I had Josh's friend on who told this encounter, but I wanted to speak to Josh to get his take on what they saw.
